Rebecca Romijn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rebecca_Romijn 0 Rebecca Alie Romijn ( roh-MAYN; Dutch: [roːˈmɛin]; born November 6, 1972) is an American actress and former model. She is known for her role as Mystique in the quadrilogy of the X-Men film series, and as Joan from The Punisher (2004), both of which are based on Marvel Comics. She also had a recurring role as Alexis Meade on the television series Ugly Betty. Her most recent major role was as Eve Baird on the TNT TV Series The Librarians, which ran for four seasons. She most recently starred as Herself in Skin Wars. Rebecca_Alie_Romijn ( roh-MAYN ; Dutch : [_roːˈmɛin_] ; born November_6_,_1972 ) is an_American_actress and former_model .
